---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Services | Kaya Blue" description="Web development services for real estate, staffing, and finance.">
<main>
<!-- Hero Section: Editorial & High-End -->
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 px-6 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full pointer-events-none">
<div class="absolute top-20 left-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 mb-8">
<span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent" style="">Core Capabilities</span>
</div>
<h1 class="text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-tighter text-white mb-8" style="">
                Architectural <br>
<span class="text-gradient" style="">Digital Solutions</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-12" style="">
                We engineer high-performance infrastructures designed for scale, security, and technical prestige. Precision is not a goal; it is our foundation.
            </p>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Merged Section: Precision Workflow & Service Modules -->
<section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto border-t border-slate-800/50">
<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16">
<!-- Left Column: Narrative Sticky -->
<div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:sticky lg:top-32 h-fit">
<h2 class="text-accent font-mono text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6" style="">Our Methodology</h2>
<h3 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-8" style="">Precision Engineered For Performance</h3>
<p class="text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10" style="">
                    Our workflow is a rigorous architectural process. We don't just "build websites"—we construct robust digital ecosystems that leverage advanced technical frameworks to solve industry-specific challenges.
                </p>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent" data-icon="check_circle" style="">check_circle</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-white uppercase text-sm tracking-widest" style="">Structural Integrity</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-text-muted" style="">Built for 99.9% uptime and zero-latency performance.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent" data-icon="check_circle" style="">check_circle</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-white uppercase text-sm tracking-widest" style="">Industry Specificity</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-text-muted" style="">Custom modules designed for Real Estate, Finance, and Staffing.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Right Column: The Integrated Roadmap -->
<div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-20">
<!-- Step 1 / Real Estate -->
<div class="relative pl-12 border-l border-slate-800">
<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-accent accent-glow"></div>
<div class="mb-6 flex items-end justify-between">
<span class="step-number" style="">01</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent text-5xl opacity-50" style="">domain</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-4" style="">Real Estate Ecosystems</h4>
<p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-8" style="">
                        Our precision workflow begins with deep integration. For Real Estate, we architect PropTech platforms that synchronize global MLS data, automate lead nurturing via custom CRMs, and offer high-fidelity VR tour capabilities.
                    </p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="p-4 glass-card rounded-xl">
<span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent block mb-2" style="">INTEGRATION</span>
<p class="text-sm text-white font-medium" style="">Global MLS Sync</p>
</div>
<div class="p-4 glass-card rounded-xl">
<span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent block mb-2" style="">AUTOMATION</span>
<p class="text-sm text-white font-medium" style="">Lead Nurture Loops</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Step 2 / Finance -->
<div class="relative pl-12 border-l border-slate-800">
<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-slate-800"></div>
<div class="mb-6 flex items-end justify-between">
<span class="step-number" style="">02</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent text-5xl opacity-50" style="">account_balance</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-4" style="">Finance Architecture</h4>
<p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-8" style="">
                        The second phase focus is on security and latency. We build financial dashboards and algorithmic interfaces designed for the modern quant. Our methodology ensures SOC-2 compliance and sub-50ms execution speeds.
                    </p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="p-4 glass-card rounded-xl">
<span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent block mb-2" style="">PERFORMANCE</span>
<p class="text-sm text-white font-medium" style="">Low-Latency API</p>
</div>
<div class="p-4 glass-card rounded-xl">
<span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent block mb-2" style="">SECURITY</span>
<p class="text-sm text-white font-medium" style="">End-to-End Encryption</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Step 3 / Staffing -->
<div class="relative pl-12 border-l border-slate-800">
<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-slate-800"></div>
<div class="mb-6 flex items-end justify-between">
<span class="step-number" style="">03</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent text-5xl opacity-50" style="">group_work</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-4" style="">Staffing Portals</h4>
<p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-8" style="">
                        Finalizing the solution with scalable infrastructure. Our high-volume ATS systems and candidate matching algorithms are designed to handle recruitment at scale, reducing the friction between talent and opportunity.
                    </p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="p-4 glass-card rounded-xl">
<span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent block mb-2" style="">SCALABILITY</span>
<p class="text-sm text-white font-medium" style="">High-Volume ATS</p>
</div>
<div class="p-4 glass-card rounded-xl">
<span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent block mb-2" style="">LOGIC</span>
<p class="text-sm text-white font-medium" style="">Matching Algorithms</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Case Study Banner -->
<section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="glass-card rounded-3xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
<div class="lg:w-2/5 h-80 lg:h-auto bg-slate-800 relative">
<img alt="Tech Architecture" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-60 mix-blend-luminosity" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCQ9VtBWYUcRITGQNRChtYim4ITocx2YDpmn4dAswxgPRlGa3YKXPJvH9gSkkmXBIpvfNsCL4XmDzk0QAF1E0CkbJePGfQcjHgi76oPaipkJmPFBSqU0y8nDk_OIsKaH45HQzJqKb61bKLTx57C1HIyztBQNJw3obo27A5e4TR7vv1vgQBYSS3r81bVS2LMmxTem2-fOOneQJ3S53pJuTVRFnjSOSthwmgx6_RSBicj_zL7_6gdqWVc5gUsxoouos2NGnDQg4W-eD4" style="">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<div class="lg:w-3/5 p-12 lg:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center">
<div class="text-accent font-mono text-xs tracking-widest mb-6" style="">IMPACT ANALYSIS 042</div>
<h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6" style="">Driving 300% Scale Growth</h3>
<p class="text-text-muted text-lg mb-8 max-w-xl" style="">
                    By rebuilding legacy trading portals into microservices-based architectures, we reduced execution latency by 45ms and allowed for 3x simultaneous user scaling.
                </p>
<div class="flex gap-12">
<div>
<div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent" style="">45ms</div>
<div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-text-muted uppercase tracking-widest" style="">Latency Drop</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent" style="">300%</div>
<div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-text-muted uppercase tracking-widest" style="">Cap Growth</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA Section (Consistent Style) -->
<section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
<div class="p-12 lg:p-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-card-dark to-primary border border-slate-800 relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-20 -mt-20 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -ml-20 -mb-20 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
<h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black mb-6 text-white" style="">Ready for a Performance Upgrade?</h2>
<p class="text-xl text-text-muted mb-10 leading-relaxed" style="">Join the elite league of digital-first enterprises. Let's architect your future together.</p>
<a href="/book-a-call" class="bg-accent text-primary px-10 py-5 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform accent-glow">Schedule Your Strategy Session</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</BaseLayout>
